Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  told it=
 not to and it didn=E2=80=99t</a>. Last October=C2=A0Coinbase put out=C2=A0=
an ambitious=C2=A0=E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
