ing on a block might call up some investors and ask them some general quest=
ions. =E2=80=9CHey how are you feeling about the tech sector today,=E2=80=
=9D the bank might ask. A smart hedge fund that is following the sector mig=
ht say =E2=80=9Caha, you have block coming for Tech Company X=E2=80=9D and =
short the stock.=C2=A0</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">A bank cons=
idering a block trade might=C2=A0<em>wall-cross </em>a few investors, askin=
