d investor agreements with long lockups, so that if any of my investors cal=
led me and said =E2=80=9Cwait is your hedge fund=E2=80=99s entire strategy =
just owning Tesla stock?=E2=80=9D I could say =E2=80=9Cyep=E2=80=9D and han=
g up without them withdrawing their money. But then I would buy as much Tes=
la as I could get, tell everyone to go home, lock the doors and come back a=
t the end of the year.=C2=A0Tesla was up a ludicrous 743% in 2020, which wo=
uld put me among the all-time greats of hedge fund performance. My performa=
