the year I would be able to pay myself=C2=A0<em>more than all of the money=
=C2=A0</em>my investors put in at the beginning of the year, and they would=
 be thrilled about it because they were up like 600% net of fees. And then =
I=E2=80=99d go back to them, ask for an even longer and stricter lockup, mo=
ve all the money into GameStop Corp. for 2021[5] and go back to the beach.<=
/p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If <em>you</em> had a hedge fund and a time=
